snippet: Rafael Nadal overcame a slow start to beat Federico Delbonis, 6-3, 6-2, for his first singles victory in seven months in the third round of the Chilean Open in Viña del Mar on Wednesday.
abstract: Rafael Nadal defeats Federico Delbonis in third-round of Chilean Open tennis tournament.
lead_paragraph: Rafael Nadal overcame a slow start to beat Federico Delbonis, 6-3, 6-2, for his first singles victory in seven months in the third round of the Chilean Open in Viña del Mar on Wednesday.
